45 and charm leveling:<BR>Sow potions or boots, some type of water breathing device, and air illusion. Go to Lake of Ill Omen.<BR>Goblins primarly spawn in two's, so charm one against the other to break the spawn. If charm breaks, float to the top of the water, run to shore, and camp if you don't wanna deal with it. (Bloodgills can't swim as fast as you can run on the water surface)<BR>I got about...4 complete levels I'd say at the 'gills. Once you hit 49 and get allure, /game over. I get one resist in about 20 casts, and can easily get everything under control. Rune4 or your str rune spell is a necessity as well.<P>--------------------<P>"One target pls!"<BR>Caenem  <BR>Caveo Ervum<BR>RZ
